highlights.text: “Hurts So Good” by Astrid S is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Kochi, up 34 spots at #65.
“Ranjithame (From "Varisu")” by Thalapathy Vijay, M.M.Manasi, and Thaman S is the highest new entry on Top Songs Kochi at #20.
Anirudh Ravichander has the most spots on Top Songs Kochi. “Thenmozhi (From "Thiruchitrambalam")” is the highest at #2.
“Munbe Vaa” by A.R. Rahman, Shreya Ghoshal, and Naresh Iyer has been on Top Songs Kochi the longest, at 56 weeks straight.
